CNCP v1 23863
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#5102: Suspense not waiting for async components using v-if",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:53.769108+00:00",
  "text": "Suspense not waiting for async components using v-if\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.26\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[sfc.vuejs.org/](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nClick the button with \"Start loading\" on it and see that the fallback on suspense is not displayed.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nThe suspense fallback slot should be displayed while the async component is loading.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nThe suspense fallback slot is not being shown.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: suspense"
  ],
